In fact, we were busier than ever now that Monica's work with the Commission on the Status of Women was in full swing.

LineNo: 6846669,

She spent most days of the week meeting with Ciara or members of the Assembly, discussing how to implement the new laws I had passed. I often had to pitch in with chores or help Deana with her homework myself.

LineNo: 6847485,

en
